doctype html
html(lang="en")
    head
        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(http-equiv='x-ua-compatible', content='ie=edge')
        title Home | Max Klopsch
        meta(name="description", content="Hey, I'm Max Klopsch. This is my personal website. I'm a full-stack web developer living in Nottingham, UK.")
        link(rel='stylesheet', href='/css/index.css')
    body
        h1 Max Klopsch | Portfolio
        h2 About me
        p Hey, I'm Max! I'm a full-stack developer living in Nottingham, UK. JavaScript, PHP, Python. HTML, CSS, jQuery. NodeJS, Express, Pug, MySQL, MongoDB. Experience working with Magento 1.xx.
        p I'm available for junior developer positions and freelance projects.
        h2 Resume
        p 
            | Check out my 
            a(href="") resume
            |  to learn more about my experience!
        h2 Certifications, Qualifications, Achievements
        ul
            li BSc Aerospace Engineering @ TU Delft in Delft, Netherlands
            li Fundamentals of Digital Marketing Certification, Google Digital Garage
        h2 Projects
        p 
            | Since July 2018 I have been studying web development with 
            a(href="https://teamtreehouse.com") Treehouse
            | . It's a great platform with easy to understand lectures and many projects you can build. Checkout my 
            a(href="https://teamtreehouse.com/maxklopsch") Treehouse profile
            |  to see my progress and skills. Below you can also find a selection of projects I have built and deployed on my website:
        p
            a(href="/four-in-a-row") Play Four In A Row
        p
            a(href="/home") "Login"
            br
            a(href="/cards") Begin Flash Card Study
        p
            a(href="/books") Bookworm app with login and user profiles
        h2 Hire me
        p 
            | I would like to work as a junior developer for a company in the East Midlands, UK or remote. I am also available to work on freelance projects, e.g. creating custom websites for you or your business. Feel free to contact me using the 
            a(href="#footer") contact form
            |  in the footer or reach out via 
            a(href="#footer") social media
            | .
        footer#footer
            div Find me on
                ul
                    li
                        a(href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/MaxKlopsch/") LinkedIn
                    li
                        a(href="https://github.com/MaxKlopsch") GitHub
                    li
                        a(href="https://teamtreehouse.com/maxklopsch") Treehouse

            div.container
                h2 Contact me
                form(method="POST", action="/contact")
                    label(for="name") Name
                    input(type="text", id="name", name="name", placeholder="Your name")
                    label(for="email") Email
                    input(type="email", id="email", name="email", placeholder="name@domain.com")
                    label(for="phone") Phone
                    input(type="tel", id="phone", name="phone", placeholder="+44 12345 67891")
                    label(for="message") Message
                    textarea(id="message", name="message", placeholder="Your message goes here...", style="height:200px")
                    input(type="submit", value="Submit")